    <item>
      <title>Principal Contradiction</title>
      <link>https://emsenn.net/library/domains/humanities/domains/philosophy/domains/western/domains/marxism/terms/principal-contradiction/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://emsenn.net/library/domains/humanities/domains/philosophy/domains/western/domains/marxism/terms/principal-contradiction/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Principal contradiction identifies which contradiction is decisive in a&#xA;conjuncture when multiple contradictions coexist. In Mao&amp;rsquo;s formulation,&#xA;this role can shift as conditions change; principal status is historical,&#xA;not eternal [@mao-on-contradiction-1937].&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This concept is strategic: it orders analytic and political priority.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;related-terms&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#related-terms&#34; class=&#34;heading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Link to this section&#34;&gt;¶&lt;/a&gt;Related terms&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://emsenn.net/library/domains/humanities/domains/philosophy/domains/western/domains/marxism/terms/secondary-contradiction/&#34; class=&#34;link-internal&#34;&gt;Secondary Contradiction&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://emsenn.net/library/domains/humanities/domains/philosophy/domains/western/domains/marxism/terms/contradiction/&#34; class=&#34;link-internal&#34;&gt;Contradiction&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://emsenn.net/library/domains/humanities/domains/philosophy/domains/western/domains/marxism/terms/historicization/&#34; class=&#34;link-internal&#34;&gt;Historicization&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Secondary Contradiction</title>
      <link>https://emsenn.net/library/domains/humanities/domains/philosophy/domains/western/domains/marxism/terms/secondary-contradiction/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://emsenn.net/library/domains/humanities/domains/philosophy/domains/western/domains/marxism/terms/secondary-contradiction/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Secondary contradictions are contradictions within a process that do not&#xA;occupy the decisive position at a given stage. They can intensify,&#xA;recede, and under changed conditions become principal&#xA;[@mao-on-contradiction-1937].&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Treating secondary contradictions as irrelevant is an error; the concept&#xA;marks subordination, not insignificance.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;related-terms&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#related-terms&#34; class=&#34;heading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Link to this section&#34;&gt;¶&lt;/a&gt;Related terms&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://emsenn.net/library/domains/humanities/domains/philosophy/domains/western/domains/marxism/terms/principal-contradiction/&#34; class=&#34;link-internal&#34;&gt;Principal Contradiction&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://emsenn.net/library/domains/humanities/domains/philosophy/domains/western/domains/marxism/terms/contradiction/&#34; class=&#34;link-internal&#34;&gt;Contradiction&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
    </item>
